<lb n="29"/>for great wisdom and prudence
<lb n="30"/>and when on his death-bed, it is
<lb n="31"/>related that he called all his
<lb n="32"/>children around him and said,
<lb n="33"/>&quot;Now in my lifetime I have searched
<lb n="34"/>most carefully through all the traditions
